00:40:13,640 --> 00:40:21,560
And then, if you said that, you were only defining something very important and nice in your world.

418
00:40:21,560 --> 00:40:24,039
Because that's still not to say they're a paradigm.

419
00:40:24,040 --> 00:40:32,279
And the reason you can tell is: what if somebody came along with more, stronger, sexier, stylish, or wittier, compassionate, smarter, and so forth?

420
00:40:32,279 --> 00:40:34,279
Well, you could just go for them.

421
00:40:34,279 --> 00:40:38,600
Because all you, because what you make a list of all the traits that you like.

