00:48:08,959 --> 00:48:13,440
But in your life, it becomes the definition that defines you.

514
00:48:13,439 --> 00:48:18,719
And like a triangle has three sides, you are the lover of the princess.

515
00:48:18,879 --> 00:48:29,039
So Kierkegaard discovers that there's not only a detached kind of necessity like a triangle has three sides, but an involved kind of necessity in a defining relation.

